(318, 53, 2, 'VOICE', '', '', NULL, 'https://kkhc.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/eps-juzibot/permanent/material/%36%61%31%64%34%61%62%63%61%61%61%30%64%30%66%34%65%32%36%30%35%31%31%66.silk', 'https://drh.likeduoduiyi.cn/homework/voice/e9d0485cd463431ba83ea6ea258841b4.mp3', 101000, NULL, NULL, 101000, 0, 'liuyuan_config_20260601', 'liuyuan_config_20260601', '2026-06-01 17:02:54.903000', '2026-06-01 19:59:44.046000'),
(319, 54, 1, 'TEXT', '', '', '看来咱们经过4天的学习，已经和当时没上课的您有很大的提升啊！但是对于技巧和方法的运用上，我再给您讲讲，您稍等 我给您发语音！', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2000, 1, 'liuyuan_config_20260601', 'liuyuan_config_20260601', '2026-06-01 17:02:55.315000', '2026-06-01 19:59:44.046000'),
(320, 54, 2, 'VOICE', '', '', NULL, 'https://kkhc.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/eps-juzibot/permanent/material/%36%61%31%64%34%61%62%66%61%61%61%30%64%30%66%34%65%32%36%30%35%33%65%63.silk', 'https://drh.likeduoduiyi.cn/homework/voice/81be9fcf22234d539b197f78ae3d488a.mp3', 84000, NULL, NULL, 84000, 0, 'liuyuan_config_20260601', 'liuyuan_config_20260601', '2026-06-01 17:02:58.253000', '2026-06-01 19:59:44.046000'),
(321, 55, 1, 'TEXT', '', '', '同学您好啊！今天是最后一节课了，赵老师还是用心给你点评，您也耐心听完赵老师讲的，我们学习不要半途而废！坚持下去！', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2000, 1, 'liuyuan_config_20260601', 'liuyuan_config_20260601', '2026-06-01 17:02:58.629000', '2026-06-01 19:59:44.046000'),
